HOW TO USE THIS: 

Open up your missions cfgspawnabletypes.xml file, and search for 'Weapons'. As of the writing of this, it is located on line 1339. 

Right above the CZ61 set up, copy all of the config text here and paste into that file. Scroll through and make sure the formatting is correct, and
make sure you didnt miss any necessary text. For help, message me on discord, Not A Banana#9930

Feel free to edit the values of the percentages. The way it works is <attachments chance=#> is the chance of the attachment to spawn, with 1.00 being
100% and 0.50 being 50%, etc, you get the idea. 

